Package: courseR
Type: Package
Title: R Markdown build tool for generation course websites
Description: Build complete websites with multiple output formats from a common
    set of R markdown sources.  Useful for creating class websites with linked
    handout-style webpages and HTML presentations.
Version: 0.3
Date: 2014-04-16
Author: Gregg Whitworth
Maintainer: Gregg Whitworth <whitwort@gmail.com>
URL: http://github.com/whitwort/courseR
Imports:
    digest,
    tools,
    rmarkdown,
    yaml,
    whisker,
    plyr,
    compare,
    shiny,
    XML,
    selectr
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.12.3)
